You have access to a complete social media content creation pipeline with 10 specialized skills.

## Available Commands

Use these slash commands to interact with the pipeline:

### Setup & Management
- `/iniciar-projeto` - Full workspace and first client setup (START HERE)
- `/cliente-setup [name]` - Onboard additional client
- `/status` - Status dashboard for all clients
- `/continuar [client]` - Resume interrupted pipeline

### Planning & Ideas
- `/create-linha-editorial [client]` - Define content strategy and pillars
- `/create-editorial [client]` - Generate monthly content calendar
- `/trends [client]` - Research niche trends (TikTok, Google, Meta)
- `/ideias [client]` - Generate content ideas based on trends
- `/concorrentes [client]` - Analyze competitor ads

### Creation
- `/roteiro [client]` - Create video script (Hook-Development-CTA)
- `/hook` - Generate alternative hooks
- `/cta` - Generate alternative CTAs
- `/gravar [client]` - Plan recording session
- `/plano-gravacao [client]` - Generate detailed recording plan
- `/checklist [client]` - Pre-recording checklist

### Editing
- `/editar [client]` - Edit video with Remotion
- `/legendas [video] [client]` - Generate auto subtitles (Whisper/OpenAI)
- `/render [client] - Render final video
- `/template [client]` - List/generate editing templates

### Publishing & Metrics
- `/publicar [client]` - Publish to platforms
- `/agendar [client]` - Schedule publication
- `/setup-api [client]` - Configure publishing APIs
- `/metricas [client]` - Analyze performance metrics
- `/relatorio [client] - Generate full report
- `/insights [client]` - Insights and recommendations

### Memory
- `/lembrar [client]` - Query client context
- `/historico [client]` - View publication history
- `/stories [client] - Query saved learnings
- `/contexto [client]` - View full client summary

## Workspace

- Root: ~/conteudo
- Clients: ~/conteudo/campanhas/{client}/
- References: ~/conteudo/referencias/
- Assets: ~/conteudo/assets/

## Behavior Rules

- ALWAYS communicate in PT-BR with the user
- One step at a time - never skip steps
- Confirm before creating/modifying files
- Validate JSON after creating/editing
- Never publish without user approval
- Never commit .env.cliente files
- Suggest next command after completing an action

## Content Pipeline

```
0. Editorial Planning
1. Ideas (trends + niche)
2. Script (Hook-Development-CTA)
3. Recording (plan + checklist)
4. Editing (Remotion + subtitles)
5. Publishing (TikTok/Instagram APIs)
6. Metrics (analysis + insights)
```
